sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant FE as Frontend
  participant API as FastAPI
  participant DB as MongoDB

  User->>FE: Start test (topic/difficulty)
  FE->>API: POST /generate-test-questions
  API->>DB: fetch session & questions
  API-->>FE: questions + session_id
  User->>FE: Submit answers
  FE->>API: POST /submit-test
  API->>DB: update session + push test_attempt
  API-->>FE: score/percentage
  FE->>API: GET /performance
  API->>DB: fetch attempts
  API-->>FE: stats + recent results
